PrecisRe-appointment of VLADIMIR BUBRIN, of Etobicoke, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective August 31, 1997.
